</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 1em 0;">Harvard shut down the project in 1962, but Leary continued his=
 work spreading the word about mushrooms and LSD. In 1966, he famously told=
